name: Last 2 Left
tag_list: social-gaming, social-networking, fantasy-games, sports, games, reality-tv
overview:
Last 2 Left is a patented fantasy game format that can be applied to all types of competitions, such as sports, reality television, stock markets, politics and tournaments, allowing for countless applications.

This game format will become the theme for a social platform by the same name, providing content and interaction far beyond games, with unlimited access points.

Future plans include:

Super simple, fantasy game format External game service for web publishers Create-your-own games and contests for local events A unique, competitive social network Niche platform featuring celebrities and related content Data feeds for third party applications
